We elect to satisfy points (a) and (c) of the Safe Harbor Enforcement Principle by committing to cooperate with the DPAs & Swiss FDPIC; 

We will cooperate with the DPAs in the investigation and resolution of complaints brought under the Safe Harbor; and 

We will comply with any advice given by the DPAs where the DPAs take the view that the organization needs to take specific action to comply with the Safe Harbor Principles, including remedial or compensatory measures for the benefit of individuals affected by any non-compliance with the Principles, and will provide the DPAs with written confirmation that such action has been taken.
